text: Josép Robert Serra (born 13 February 1967) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pla de l'Estany Category:Catalan sportspeople
